                            <h4 style="color:black">Best choice</h4>
                            <p style="color:black">CHAO MAO BIRDCLUB gives you suitable accommodation options for you to have a wonderful bird hobby.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-4 d-flex my-5">
                        <div class="image">
                            <img src="~/images/security.png" alt="security">
                        </div>
                        <div class="content">
                            <h4 style="color:black">Safety & security</h4>
