                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-4 d-flex  my-5">
                        <div class="image">
                            <img src="~/images/support.png" alt="img3">
                        </div>
                        <div class="content">
                            <h4 style="color:black">Support 24/7</h4>
                            <p style="color:black">Always listen, always support you with all services at CHAO MAO BIRDCLUB.</p>
                        </div>
